{"page_content": "![](https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/_assets/3137b1a864c689786cac76b3def62dd1/Assets/img/default-banner.jpg)\n\nObtaining a Licence\n\n# Motorcycle (6A, 6B, 6C) and 3-Wheel (6E)\n\nTo obtain a Class 6A, 6B or 6C motorcycle driver's licence, you have to pass a knowledge test, take a course, and pass 2 road tests.\n\nTo obtain a Class 6E licence, which authorizes you to ride 3-wheel motorcycles, you must hold a Class 5 licence and complete a one-day training course.\n\nLast update: July 16, 2025\n\n## Safety first, on the road and online\n\nWe are committed to protecting your personal information and privacy. That's why, when we collect data, we follow a [Policy on Privacy](https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/policies/privacy) that is responsible and transparent. By continuing to browse without modifying your preferences, you accept the use of cookies.\n\nEdit settingsAcceptReject\n\nDÃ©tection du zoom", "metadata": {"title": "Motorcycle (6A, 6B, 6C) and 3-Wheel (6E) - SAAQ", "description": "There are 3 licence classes to drive heavy vehicles: Class 1 for combinations of road vehicles, Class 2 for buses and Class 3 for trucks.", "url": "https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/drivers-licences/obtaining-licence/motorcycle-6a-6b-6c-6e", "language": "en", "keywords": "heavy vehicle driver's licence, driving a heavy vehicle, obtaining heavy vehicle licence, heavy vehicle licence, bus licence, truck licence, road train licence", "robots": null, "og_title": "Heavy Vehicle Driver's Licence (Class 1, 2 or 3)", "og_description": "There are 3 licence classes to drive heavy vehicles: Class 1 for combinations of road vehicles, Class 2 for buses and Class 3 for trucks.", "og_url": "https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/en/drivers-licences/obtaining-licence/motorcycle-6a-6b-6c-6e", "og_image": "https://saaq.gouv.qc.ca/_assets/3137b1a864c689786cac76b3def62dd1/Assets/img/og.png", "og_audio": null, "og_determiner": null, "og_locale": null, "og_locale_alternate": null, "og_site_name": "SAAQ", "og_video": null, "